cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel approach that uses a convolutional neural network for automatic feature extraction in reinforcement learning applied to residential load control. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-categories.
